  Protracker1.1b replayer.
- If you still use the reqtools.library - the filename will appear  automati-
  cally.   (Hey Marley!).  The  filename  looks  like:  MOD.INFECT RULEZ!  or
  KRIS.KILLER . The signs (e.g. MOD./FC14./SONIC./)  are added automatically.
  If the module has no name, the final name is also NoName!


